Snare Glands Aggro Trick- <br>
<br>
Snare Glands are available form the Caller Quest in FG. All you need is 2 minimum. <br>
<br>
This is the fastest way to gain quick aggro on an MT switch or such w/o AE Taunt. Burn as many charges as you want untill you get solid aggro. <br>
<br>
once its empty you can RECHARGE it. Goto a vendor with 1 empty gland and 1 full one. Sell the Empty one to vendor (make sure he has space). Then sell him the full one. You can then buy both back with full charges. You should farm 10-20 of them and use for big fights if aggro control on MT switch is a problem. <br>
